social_posts.post_text: Got a few days of riding in between rains. Loving this little very talented feisty mare. She loves to jump and has the biggest heart. She’s definitely going to teach me a lot. I definitely need to strengthen my core in order to be able to ride her properly. I guess that is going to be one of my New Year’s Resolutions that I need to start now. #ruethewarmblood🕊 #ruethewarmblood #hunterjumper #loveher
Had so much fun playing Chase Me Charlie on our Funday. This little mare is so much fun to ride. #ruethewarmblood🕊 #ruethewarmblood #hunterjumper #christmasfun #christmas #chasemecharlie
D got to have his own Christmas Funday.🎄He’s such a cutie.😍 #seasonsgreetings #happyholidays #merrychristmas🎄 #ottb @zlequestrian @o3animalhealth
Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays! Hope everyone has a wonderful holiday.🎄😍 #happyholidays #merrychristmas #romanthemiraclehorse #ruethewarmblood

It was nice to get a ride in before the rain. Rue was very fresh. I’m not going to lie it’s not easy for me to ride Rue. She’s so talented and a lot of horse. She likes to be the boss and I’m learning how to handle that. Sometimes it’s hard when your lacking experience to connect with a horse properly. I just have to keep practicing and there’s no doubt that she’s going to teach me how to really ride. She is such a sweet girl with a very strong mind.💙💪🕊 #ruethewarmblood #ruethewarmblood🕊 #hunterjumper #bossmare #warmblood

Wishing you and your family a new year filled with good health, happiness, love, peace, fun, and great adventures. Every day is a gift and as I get older I become more and more grateful for being able share my life and have so much fun with such a wonderful barn family and all their incredible horses. 2022 was full of so many changes for us. If it wasn’t for our fearless leader @zlequestrian we wouldn’t be taking this incredible ride together. We love you.💙Happy New Year!🥳 #grateful #happynewyear #newyear #thoroughbred #hunterjumper

Roman’s hoof 4 months ago and the transformation to today. To me it’s nothing short of a miracle. I’m so happy for him. Has the journey been easy? Not exactly but I know it’s worth it for his health. We had a few setbacks with an abscess and a bit of bruising but he is incredibly sound and is walking like a freight train. Before we pulled his shoes we were told he probably wouldn’t do well without shoes. It just goes to show what really good hay, supplements, trimming, and lots of movement can do. Thanks @zlequestrian for the guidance and keeping his hooves trimmed up. I have to say you are pretty darn good at this natural barefoot farrier thing.💙 Also thanks to @cavallohoofboots for all the support during this transition. He couldn’t have done it without your boots. #barefoot #happyhooves #naturalbarefoottrimming #naturalbarefoothoofcare #romanthemiraclehorse

Dreaming about the day we can do this again.💙There’s been so much rain we haven’t really been able to ride. These were from our Christmas funday. Thanks for the photos @arii.eq ❤️ #hunterjumper #warmblood #ruethewarmblood #ruethewarmblood🕊
Enjoy Zynnie doing a little birthday dance for @zlequestrian today. Happy Birthday Zoey! Love you🥳💙 #happybirthday
Bynxy and Rue were taking an afternoon nap yesterday and wanted to snuggle. They were so sweet. Thanks @randi_eq 📹💙 #sleepytime ##snuggle #ruethewarmblood #ruethewarmblood🕊 #hunterjumper #happyhorses
First real ride on Rue🕊 in about a month. She was feeling a bit feisty and we are both out of shape but it was fun to finally ride again.💙 #hunterjumper #warmblood #ruethewarmblood #ruethewarmblood🕊

Just very grateful to be able to ride this horse. She is so sweet, so honest, and so very talented. Like I’ve said before she is not an easy horse for me to ride and sometimes pushes me out of my comfort zone. I guess that’s why I’m feeling more grateful as each day passes. Being a surfer most of my life has taught me that you have to put in a lot of time to learn how to sync with the energy of a wave, which I find is very similar with a horse. For me it takes so much courage, patience, and determination. Is it always easy? Definitely not! There are great rewards in learning how to deal with the unpredictable. I have so much to learn from this horse and just maybe as I become a better rider I can help her become a better horse too. She’s definitely special and has the biggest heart when she jumps. I just love that about her.💙#loveher #ruethewarmblood #ruethewarmblood🕊 #hunterjumper #warmblood @o3animalhealth

Just a few sweet moments with the cutest boy. The girls and I played Roman’s favorite game yesterday and he just loved it. #happyboy #happyhorse #romanthemiraclehorse @o3animalhealth 📹 @mercedesnatalia 💙

Had a fun lesson on Rue yesterday. Though some moments were definitely better than others. I did my first bounce. I feel it really helps Rue focus on what we are doing. She tends gets a little preoccupied on other things when I’m riding her. I’m looking forward to doing more grids and bounces to help us both. Also loving my new Stubben saddle.💙 #hunterjumper #ruethewarmblood #ruethewarmblood🕊 #onedayatatime @equestrianclubshop @stubbenna @stubben_ca

I always look forward to my jump lesson on Saturday’s. Rue definitely felt good with some boots on. I was struggling to stay with her powerful jump but it’s always fun to jump this little powerhouse mare. #ruethewarmblood #ruethewarmblood🕊 #hunterjumper #warmblood @equestrianclubshop @o3animalhealth

It’s been forever since I posted because of this crazy weather. Well hopefully we are looking forward to brighter days with a lot more fun with the horses. Our turnouts are finally dry enough to use. Enjoy Roman’s uncoordinated attempt to get some of his energy out. #romanthemiraclehorse

Well I did a thing today. Welcome to the family Courtisane Z. I’ll call him Zephyr around the barn. He’s a 17.2 hand Zangersheide that was imported from Europe about 5 years ago. He is the absolute sweetest boy and I’m already so in love with him. I’m just so very grateful to own such an incredible horse. Thank you @zlequestrian for finding him and making me see that we are meant for each other. Also for helping to make it all happen.💙Also thanks to my amazing husband @tonylunafish whom has always supported whatever crazy dream I’ve had.💙I know you already love him as much as I do. And thanks to our barn family for encouraging me to go for it.💙Just so you all know, I wasn’t looking to get another horse. In a turn of events, it just happened. I’m so excited for all the fun we will have together.💙 #zangersheide #hunterjumper #welcometothefamily #courtisanez
I found a picture of baby Zephyr.🥰💙 #zephyr🦕 #courtizanez #zangersheide #hunterjumper

It was so fun to finally ride yesterday. It’s a pretty incredible feeling to get on a horse after he’s done nothing but walking for almost 3 weeks and have him be such a good boy. He’s just so sweet.🦕💙Also he was sick for a week then I had his shoes pulled a few days ago. His feet have a long road ahead to reshape and heal but I think he will do great. He has really deep sulcus thrush and that will need lots of time to heal. As you can see he looks pretty darn sound just 3 days after having his shoes pulled. We are going to take it slowly and just see how he feels. Definitely going to get him some @cavallohoofboots 💙 #hunterjumper #happyhorse #happyhooveshappyhorse #zangersheide #zephyr🦕 #dreamhorse #warmblood #lovehim #barefootjourney

Had a fun little lesson on Zephyr.🦕💙It’s so exciting when I learn something new. I definitely have lots to work on but that’s what makes it’s so fun. Now that the weather is nice, I’m looking forward to all of us horse people being able to start riding more. Thanks @zlequestrian for the cutest picture of my boy.💙 #zangersheide #warmblood #hunterjumper #zephyrthezangersheide🦕

It was a gorgeous day and I had a fun lesson. I’m sure enjoying getting to know this wonderful horse.💙It’s only been three weeks since we pulled his shoes so we’re taking it slowly as far as jumping. It was sure nice to pop over a few cross rails. #grateful #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #hunterjumper #happyhorse @o3animalhealth

Took Zephyr on his first little trail ride. He was very excited to see some new sights but the best boy. Thanks to the best trail guides Troy and @zlequestrian #happytrails #hunterjumper #zephyrthezangersheide🦕

Baby steps for Zephyr and I. Did my first baby oxer yesterday. It’s a joy learning on this sweet horse. He has a lot of energy but it’s a really good energy.💙#grateful #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #hunterjumper #warmblood @equestrianclubshop @o3animalhealth
Had lots of fun this week learning new things and getting to know this sweet boy.💙 #feelinghappy #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #hunterjumper @o3animalhealth
Did I ever mention how big Zephyr is?💙 #bigboy #zephyrthezangersheide🦕

Went for a schooling day at El Sueno. Zephyr was pretty excited to be there. It’s always fun to try new things with him. #zangershiedewarmblood #hunterjumper #elsuenoequestriancenter #zephyrthezangersheide🦕

I often get nervous on approach to a jump and get busy with my hands. We are working on half halting a few strides before a jump and then getting me to relax. It felt good to have a nice rhythm and relax. Now if I can just remember to do it on every jump.😳Im sure gonna try💙 #zephyrthezangershiede #warmblood #barefoot #hunterjumper
Zoey put my last fence up to 2’9” and it was really fun to do something over 2’. Zephyr is so big, he makes it look so tiny.🦕 #bighorseproblems😂 #zangersheide #hunterjumper #zephyrthezangersheide🦕

Have you ever had a lesson that started out great and then you just couldn’t do anything right half way through it? That was me yesterday.🤦‍♀️This video was the beginning of my jump lesson and I will spare you the end. I lost my focus and let my lack of self confidence get the best of me after getting a few bad distances. I also broke both of my hoof boots. I guess sometimes we just have those days. #stillsograteful❤️ #alwayslearning #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #hunterjumper

So nothing new to post. Our ring is getting new footing this week. I’ve been riding Zephyr bare back when my knee hurts to much to put in a stirrup. It’s crazy how I’m a bit saddle sore the next day. I’m guessing it’s helping to strengthen different muscles I never use. I honestly love it so much more than being in a saddle. To bad it’s impossible for me to do a decent posting trot so I mostly just canter.😂 #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #bareback #hunterjumper #warmblood
Roman doing his Roman things.😂💙 #happyhorse #joy #romanthemiraclehorse

Silly song I know but riding a 17.2 horse sometimes poses it’s problems when it comes to handiness. Zephyr was so good when we tried this little exercise. I think this will be about as handy as we can get. Can’t wait to get some jumps back in our ring. This was from last month. #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #hunterjumper #belgiumwarmblood #warmblood @o3animalhealth

So much love for this horse.🦕💙I had two amazing lessons this week and learned so many new things. Since @zlequestrian is interested in doing some Eventing we’ve all been doing some Dressage tests. It’s so rewarding but really hard work. It’s just so much fun. #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #warmblood #belgiumwarmblood #hunterjumper
Happy Independence Day! ❤️🤍💙 #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #happyhorse #hunterjumper #warmblood #independenceday
It finally feels like summer.☀️Hoping everyone is finding a way to stay cool. Loving my new shirt from @equestrianclubshop #hunterjumper #zephyrthewarmblood🦕 @o3animalhealth

Well I got on Roman today for the first time in about a year. We never did much more than walking because he was just to busy being a naughty boy. The one thing I love about Roman is that he’s finds joy in everything he does. He’s always making Zoey and I laugh because he is such a funny character. #romanthemiraclehorse 👑 #happyboy # hunterjumper
Just so grateful this sweet boy came into my life.💙 #feelinggrateful #happyhorse #lovehim #zephyrthezangersheide🦕

Had a fun lesson on Zephyr today.💙We both need to work on our fitness so it’s time to set some goals. Building muscle and getting rid of our hay bellies.😁💙 #hunterjumper #zangersheide #zephyrthezangersheide🦕
Happy Labor Day weekend! Hope everyone has a super fun weekend! #laborday #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 #hunterjumper

We had such a fun day at Rincon. I’ve been surfing there for the last 45 years and it was pretty special to be able to ride on my favorite beach. The weather was so beautiful. I decided not to take Zephyr because I wasn’t sure I could handle his excitement.😂I was lucky to be able to catch a quick ride on this cute little horse Puma. Good times with amazing humans and the best horses.💙 #beachride🐴 #rincon #feelinggrateful❤️

We had such a fun schooling day at El Sueno. Still learning so much and really wanting to build a solid partnership with my sweet boy. He had lots of happy energy which can intimidate me but we worked through it. I came away feeling like we learned so much and I think Zephyr really enjoyed himself. Thanks @zlequestrian for taking us on such fun adventures and also for helping me learn how to ride this amazing creature.💙 #hunterjumper #zangershide #equestrian #zephyrthezangersheide🦕 @o3animalhealth

I’m so excited to try my new Arro Helmet. It looks so amazing and it’s the only helmet with both the MIPS and the SNELL safety standards. It’s so great that it has 2 detachable/interchangeable visors. Thank you so much @arrohelmets 💙 #equestrianhelmets #helmet #eventing #hunterjumper #helmetsafety #safetyfirst #equestrianhelmet

We had such a great day playing with the horses at El Sueno. This doesn’t seem like much but such a proud moment today when Zephyr decided to finally walk through the water. The last two times we were there he didn’t really want to go in, but today with a little patience and @zlequestrian and Troy leading the way, he went in. It’s the little things that make me happy.😍 #happyhorse #hunterjumper #zangersheide #zephyrthezangersheide🦕

We always have so much fun when we go to El Sueno. It’s so rewarding getting to know this horse. He has the biggest heart and such a playful kind spirit. What can I say, I just adore him. Thank you @zlequestrian for helping me find the courage to do this sport. It’s just so much fun. Also thank you Troy for being there to keep Zephyr company. He’s the best buddy.
